info.name: Dark Orange by Biller
info.description: A clean dark orange theme for youtube. [MAKE SURE TO ENABLE DARK THEME FROM YOUTUBE] Feel free to leave a feedback and any donation will be appreciated. Thank you very much for your support!
info.additionalInfo: v2.8.2 | Mini-update part2. @ 26/04/2021 ------ Youtube: > Updated join and vote buttons' color for better visibility. > Updated subscribe/unsubscribe buttons. > Fixed a bug that the author's background at the comment section was light gray. ~> Changed the border for better visibility as well. > Fixed a bug that some borders was gray instead of orange. ~ Known bugs ~ > Like/Dislike button's circle border doesn't contain the text as expected. ====== v2.8.1 | Mini-update part1. @ 02/04/2021 ------ Youtube: > Changed yellow color to a darker one. > Changed some borders for better visibility. > Changed Search icon's opacity for better visibility. > Fixed updated autoplay button at the end of the video for better visibility. > Fixed updated tooltips. > Fixed Author's border in comments. > Fixed a bug that some highlighted texts were default style. > Fixed a bug that Buy/Rent button was blue instead of orange. > Fixed a bug that watch history button was blue instead of orange. ~ Known bugs ~ > Like/Dislike button's circle border doesn't contain the text as expected. ====== v2.7 | Minor update. @ 05/02/2021 ------ Youtube: > Changed filter, like and other buttons' indicators for better visibility. > Added tags' borders for better visibility as well. > Fixed a bug that some texts were blue instead of orange. > Added yellow color for the "already searched" in the search bar (for chrome users). ====== v2.6 | Changes & Fixes. @ 04/12/2020 ------ Youtube: > Added color on new auto-play button while it is enable. > Added color on new Chapters feature. > Added color on "new" tag of a new video. > Changed background color on suggested videos for better visibility. > Changed background color on "Live" Label on thumbnails. (testing) > Fixed a bug that the loop's color was back to default. > Fixed several bugs with the highlighted text. > Fixed a bug that the dot at the new notifications was blue instead of orange. ====== v2.5 | Small Changes. @ 04/11/2020 ------ Youtube: > Fixed a bug that the highlighted text was blue & white instead of orange & gray. > Changed some buttons color for better visibility. ====== v2.4 | Bug Fixes. @ 09/10/2020 ------ Youtube: > Fixed a bug that the Live chat was white instead of orange. > Fixed a bug with the "LIVE NOW" indicator. > Changed the background of the panels at the end of the video to transparent and the text color to orange for better visibility. Youtube Studio: > Fixed a bug that some panels at Dashboard & Customization were white. > Fixed a bug that the Audio Library had white background. ====== v2.3 | Bug Fixes. @ 09/09/2020 ------ Youtube: > Fixed a bug that some icons, texts and borders were gray instead of orange. > Changed the progress bar's color on hover at the video for better visibility. > Fixed a bug that the background color of the title of the video's thumbnail was gray. ~> Added an orange border on hover of the thumbnail. > "LIVE NOW" has circle border. ~> Fixed a bug that the background of the arrow at the chat was blue. > Added a border to "Reminder ON" button. > Fixed a bug that the "UNDO" button was blue instead of orange. ~ Known bugs ~ > Sometimes, the "Join" button has blue border instead of orange. ====== v2.2 | minor changes. @ 23/08/2020 ------ Youtube: > Changed some borders for better visibility. > Fixed a bug that the play button on thumbnails was white instead of orange. > Author background color changed to orange. > "Customize Channel" page updated. ~ Known bugs ~ > Sometimes, the "Join" button has blue border instead of orange. ====== v2.1 | another mini-update. @ 15/07/2020 ------ Youtube: > Thumbnails changes. ~> Time color text changed to orange. ~> Play button color changed to orange. > Fixed a bug that an orange dot appeared after hovering on thumbnails. > Fixed a bug that the "Subscribe" button was at default settings in some cases. > Added selection color (for testing). Youtube Studio: > Fixed some texts color for not getting orange color. ~ Known bugs ~ > Sometimes, the "Join" button has blue border instead of orange. ====== v2.0 | Youtube Studio update. @ 28/06/2020 ------ Youtube: > Changed the color of the "Report search predictions". > Added style to recommendation tags. > New design for Selected tabs. ~> Selected tab has a box indicator. > Added new design for Tooltips. > Sub button border added. ~> "Subscribe" button has a square shape border. ~> "Subscribed" button has a barrel shape border. > Join button border changed. > Changed the colors of the poll section. > Fixed Live chat colors. > Fixed a bug that search bar was blue instead of orange. > Fixed a bug that the search bar had white bars and the result's words were gray instead of orange. > Fixed a bug that the video slider was red instead of orange. Youtube Studio: > Added dark style for Youtube Studio. ~ Known bugs ~ > Sometimes, the "Join" button has blue border instead of orange. > There is an orange dot on top right. ====== v1.3 | 3rd update. @ 11/06/2020 ------ > Fixed a bug that notification list was white instead of orange. > Changed channel tabs from white to orange. ~> Selected tab is white. ~> Selected tab has an orange indicator under the text. > Channel sort list is now orange. > Next video's circle color is now orange. ~ Known bugs ~ > Sometimes, the search bar has white bars and the result's words are gray instead of orange. > Sometimes, the video slider is red instead of orange. ====== v1.2 | 2nd update. @ 02/06/2020 ------ > Fixed several items for not getting white color on hover. > Changed sub button. ~ Known bugs ~ > Sometimes, the search bar has white bars and the result's words are gray instead of orange. > Sometimes, the video slider is red instead of orange. ====== v1.1 | 1st update. @ 29/05/2020 ------ > White color on hover added. > Indicator for toggle buttons added. > "Add to.." list color updated for better experience. > "See more" button border removed. ~ Known bugs ~ > Sometimes, the search bar has white bars and the result's words are gray instead of orange. ====== v1.0 | Release of the theme. @ 27/05/2020 I will try to keep it updated.
